    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Searching for a car that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? Look no further \u2014 this beauty is in absolutely mint condition! We're talking flawless inside and out, with meticulous maintenance, zero issues, and the kind of care that's genuinely rare to find on the used market. Every surface, every system, every detail has been looked after with pride. If you want the very best without buying brand new, this is your opportunity \u2014 don't let it slip away!",
      "price": 47500.0,
